  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Each patient is preoperatively treated once profylactic with intraveneous antibiotics.
      Postoperatively, one group will be treated with intraveneous antibiotics during 5 days. The
      other group will receive no antibiotics.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
